00:39:41,520 --> 00:39:41,840
Aha.

550
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:43,120
A dobro.

551
00:39:43,760 --> 00:39:44,160
Da, da.

552
00:39:44,640 --> 00:39:46,160
Zato ti velim, šest izdanja.

553
00:39:46,560 --> 00:39:48,240
Božan, božan.

554
00:39:50,240 --> 00:39:54,320
Pa da, pa zato velim, možda ljudi razmišljaju ono, Bože, da je to.

555
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:55,760
A dobro.

556
00:39:56,320 --> 00:39:56,880
Kule i bile.

557
00:39:58,480 --> 00:39:59,280
A ono niste.

558
00:40:00,640 --> 00:40:01,920
Dovoljno za normalan život.

559
00:40:02,240 --> 00:40:02,320
Da.

560
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:03,760
I to je to.

